T02D1458:5b-1: shr'i sa ha dza sa bar sva tishtha nam n'a ma /
T02D1458:5b-3: dpal lhan gci skyes pa bde ba'i mchog bdag byin gyis brlab pa zhes bya ba /
T02D1458:5b-4: he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D1458:5b-5: kye ho sgrub pa'i snying po bde chen rang gi sems //
T02D1458:5b-6: 'khrul ba'i dbang gis rkyen dang bcas gyur kyang //
T02D1458:5b-7: rgya mtshe'i chu ni dang sa ma'i rang bzhin yin //
T02D1458:5b-8: rnyog ma'i rang bzhin glo bur rkyen las byung //
T02D1458:5b-9: ma bcos rang sar bzhag na rgyal ba'i thugs //
T02D1458:5b-10: 'di na bla ma'i dus thabs bsten las byung ba ste //
T02D1458:5b-11: thabs kyi rgyal po bya ba thams cad gtang bar bya'o //
T02D1458:5b-12: zhes ri khrod pa chen pos gsungs so //
